fields.description:
Expose the token_transaction table with an API in payment_selector _service



GET

/payment/selector/tokenization/clients/{clientId}/transactions/{tokenTransactionId}

Header:

|{color:#bf2600}*Auth audience:* {color}{{fs-payment}}
{color:#bf2600}*Auth scope:* {color}{{token:read}}|

response payload:

{noformat}TokenTransactionResponse{
  tokenTransactionid: uuid,
  status: String,
  responseCode: String?,
  responseMsg: String?
}{noformat}

